       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. KYCSCHED2.
      * KYC REFRESH DUE-DATE COMPUTATION (YEAR ARITHMETIC)
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-RISK                   PIC X(1) VALUE SPACE.
       01  WS-LAST-KYC-YYYY          PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-DUE-YYYY               PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-PRINT-AREA.
           05  WS-PRINT-LINE OCCURS 30 PIC X(7).
       01  FILLER                    PIC X(7) VALUE SPACES.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-RISK
           ACCEPT WS-LAST-KYC-YYYY
           PERFORM 2000-DUE
           DISPLAY 'DUE: ' WS-DUE-YYYY
           STOP RUN.
       2000-DUE.
           EVALUATE WS-RISK
             WHEN 'H' COMPUTE WS-DUE-YYYY = WS-LAST-KYC-YYYY + 2
             WHEN 'M' COMPUTE WS-DUE-YYYY = WS-LAST-KYC-YYYY + 8
             WHEN OTHER COMPUTE WS-DUE-YYYY = WS-LAST-KYC-YYYY + 10
           END-EVALUATE.
